items.title: Yanks among those interested in Ohtani
items.summary: With the Yankees continuing to fight for postseason position, it spoke volumes that Brian Cashman recently visited Japan to watch Shohei Ohtani -- "the Japanese Babe Ruth" -- take the mound.
